00:06:59.857 --> 00:07:01.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>How much do you know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about carbon reaction chambers?</c.bg_transparent>

104
00:07:02.293 --> 00:07:04.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've learned</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a little about laser-induced fusion</c.bg_transparent>

105
00:07:04.571 --> 00:07:05.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>not much more than the basics.</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:07:06.113 --> 00:07:07.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, it's a bloody inefficient system.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:07:07.870 --> 00:07:10.132 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd trade it in for a Federation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>model tomorrow if I could</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:07:10.290 --> 00:07:11.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>but it's all we've got.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:07:11.809 --> 00:07:12.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do me a favor.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:07:12.849 --> 00:07:15.171 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keep an eye on the exhaust</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>plasma temperature.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:07:17.328 --> 00:07:22.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, increase deuterium flow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by five percent to reaction chamber two.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:07:22.286 --> 00:07:24.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Procedure is not recommended.</i></c.bg_transparent>

113
00:07:24.205 --> 00:07:26.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, I've had enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of your opinions, damn it.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:07:26.655 --> 00:07:27.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just do it!</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:07:28.048 --> 00:07:28.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Procedure is not recommended.</i></c.bg_transparent>

116
00:07:29.104 --> 00:07:35.028 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Consult Cardassian operational guidelines</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>paragraph 254-A, now on screen.</i></c.bg_transparent>

117
00:07:35.324 --> 00:07:39.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to read your tech manual.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Fine. We'll do it ourselves.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:07:42.202 --> 00:07:43.721 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reinitializing reactor two.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:07:44.800 --> 00:07:48.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Directing plasma flow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to conduits 143, 144...</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:07:49.639 --> 00:07:51.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief O'Brien, the power</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>flow from reactor two</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:07:51.843 --> 00:07:52.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>has just been shut down.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:07:53.236 --> 00:07:53.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What?</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:07:54.237 --> 00:07:56.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, analyze reactor two failure.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:07:56.823 --> 00:07:58.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Reactor two was shut down</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>after sensors detected</i></c.bg_transparent>

125
00:07:59.622 --> 00:08:02.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>a potential overload</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>of the carbon reaction chambers.</i></c.bg_transparent>

126
00:08:03.703 --> 00:08:05.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's it. That's the straw!</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:08:05.534 --> 00:08:07.236 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Relax, Chief. It's just a computer.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:08:07.908 --> 00:08:10.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is no computer. This is my archenemy.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:08:10.631 --> 00:08:12.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've got it working just fine,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as far I can tell.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:08:12.831 --> 00:08:15.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fine? With all due respect, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:08:15.731 --> 00:08:17.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As an engineer,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I couldn't look at myself in the mirror</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:08:17.852 --> 00:08:20.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>if I allowed this computer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to continue to perform as it is now.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:08:21.491 --> 00:08:22.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have to do a root canal.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:08:23.050 --> 00:08:23.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Root canal?</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:08:23.890 --> 00:08:26.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's engineering shorthand, sir.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have to get into its guts.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:08:26.931 --> 00:08:29.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-and rebuild it from the ground up.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-How long will that take?</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:08:30.470 --> 00:08:32.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm still not that familiar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with Cardassian technology</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:08:32.008 --> 00:08:34.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but, oh, I guess no more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than two, three years.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:08:35.264 --> 00:08:38.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's going to take a lot of man-hours.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Is it really necessary?</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:08:38.715 --> 00:08:40.096 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't understand--</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:08:40.103 --> 00:08:42.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's just say I don't have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your sensitivity to the computer.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:08:43.902 --> 00:08:45.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's all right. Forget about it.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:08:45.621 --> 00:08:47.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Uh, Chief...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's all right. It doesn't matter.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:08:47.461 --> 00:08:50.060 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief, I want you to do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you have to do.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:08:51.219 --> 00:08:52.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you, sir. I'll get right on it.</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:08:54.658 --> 00:08:58.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And this is Ops.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The heart and soul of Deep Space 9.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:08:59.217 --> 00:09:00.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, there you are, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:09:01.537 --> 00:09:03.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Gentlemen, Madam Ambassador.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:09:03.936 --> 00:09:06.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They insisted on seeing operations, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:09:06.735 --> 00:09:07.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course.</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:09:08.214 --> 00:09:11.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Make yourselves at home.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I trust that Doctor Bashir</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:09:11.336 --> 00:09:13.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>has been taking care of all your needs.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:09:15.071 --> 00:09:18.133 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, he refuses to change</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my accommodations.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:09:18.133 --> 00:09:18.692 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Accommodations?</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:09:18.692 --> 00:09:20.944 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, if I have to sleep another night</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:09:20.944 --> 00:09:24.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>on a Cardassian bed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with gargoyles staring at me</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:09:24.620 --> 00:09:25.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>from the wood poles...</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:09:25.746 --> 00:09:26.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:09:27.029 --> 00:09:29.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>An unidentified vessel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is coming through the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:09:30.331 --> 00:09:31.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On screen. Excuse me.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:09:32.627 --> 00:09:34.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh, you'll get a better view</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from over here.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:09:43.224 --> 00:09:44.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quite a sight isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:09:46.143 --> 00:09:48.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's it? That's the whole thing?</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:09:49.143 --> 00:09:49.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, yes, it is.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:09:50.582 --> 00:09:52.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was expecting more, somehow.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:09:52.621 --> 00:09:55.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: Scanners aren't picking up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any life-forms on board.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:09:55.846 --> 00:09:58.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-A probe?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Might be.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:09:58.300 --> 00:10:00.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm reading an extensive computer array</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:10:00.519 --> 00:10:03.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but no signals to suggest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's trying to maintain contact</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:10:03.201 --> 00:10:03.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>with a mother ship.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:10:04.198 --> 00:10:05.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are the computers compatible with ours?</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:10:06.708 --> 00:10:07.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's hard to tell.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:10:08.237 --> 00:10:10.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't recognize any known</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>subprocessor patterns.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:10:11.036 --> 00:10:13.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Obviously, the young woman</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>doesn't have the necessary experience.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:10:13.475 --> 00:10:14.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps I can--</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:10:14.394 --> 00:10:18.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The "young woman" over there</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has over 300 years experience, Ambassador.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:10:18.755 --> 00:10:22.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: I might have better luck</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if we towed it into the docking ring.</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:10:22.273 --> 00:10:24.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, not until we know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a little bit more about it.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:10:25.251 --> 00:10:27.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Major, tow it to 500 meters</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>off the docking ring.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:10:27.731 --> 00:10:28.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:10:28.874 --> 00:10:31.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mr. O'Brien, try to set up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>an adaptive interface link</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:10:31.110 --> 00:10:33.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and see if we can download</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any information from it.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:10:33.429 --> 00:10:34.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:10:37.149 --> 00:10:39.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think it will be best</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if we clear this area.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:10:40.247 --> 00:10:42.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But this probe may represent contact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with a new species.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:10:43.186 --> 00:10:44.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander, I think it would be appropriate</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:10:44.747 --> 00:10:48.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>for at least one Federation ambassador</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be present at this historic occasion</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:10:48.746 --> 00:10:51.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and since I have a particular interest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in First Contact procedures...</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:10:51.748 --> 00:10:53.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I appreciate your interest, Ambassador</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:10:54.124 --> 00:10:56.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and to keep you all informed,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm scheduling a briefing</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:10:56.865 --> 00:11:01.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>at 0400. In the meantime, Dr. Bashir</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the best place to view this probe</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:11:01.421 --> 00:11:03.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>is from the docking ring near Port Seven.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:11:04.401 --> 00:11:05.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll show them the way.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:11:16.157 --> 00:11:17.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:11:29.394 --> 00:11:31.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Such concentration.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:11:31.651 --> 00:11:34.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Such intensity, such passion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for your work.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:11:35.211 --> 00:11:37.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tracking intergalactic malefactors.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:11:39.129 --> 00:11:41.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Most people find it rather tedious.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:11:41.569 --> 00:11:44.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tedious? ( chuckling )</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:11:44.383 --> 00:11:47.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, those of us who have been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>beneficiaries of your heroism</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:11:48.381 --> 00:11:50.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>would never call your work tedious.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:11:50.446 --> 00:11:51.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've learned that, on this station</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:11:52.305 --> 00:11:56.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you are the thin, beige line</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>between order and chaos.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:11:57.645 --> 00:11:58.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's my job.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:11:59.703 --> 00:12:04.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, what can I do for you?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You haven't lost anything else, I hope.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:12:05.142 --> 00:12:06.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Only my heart.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:12:07.301 --> 00:12:08.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I beg your pardon?</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:12:09.541 --> 00:12:10.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is, um...</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:12:11.520 --> 00:12:13.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is Odo your first or last name?</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:12:15.532 --> 00:12:15.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:12:16.925 --> 00:12:18.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh. Then I can just call you, uh?</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:12:19.118 --> 00:12:19.918 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:12:21.318 --> 00:12:23.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It has a certain lyrical quality.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:12:24.877 --> 00:12:25.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lyrical?</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:12:26.196 --> 00:12:27.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo...</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:12:27.555 --> 00:12:29.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It rolls off the tongue.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:12:30.594 --> 00:12:31.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh...</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:12:32.415 --> 00:12:34.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have a lot of work to do.</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:12:35.374 --> 00:12:36.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand you're a shape-shifter.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:12:38.087 --> 00:12:38.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's correct.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:12:38.933 --> 00:12:40.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've never been with a shape-shifter.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:12:42.612 --> 00:12:43.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Been with?"</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:12:44.411 --> 00:12:46.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've heard</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you're the only one of your kind.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:12:48.610 --> 00:12:49.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So far.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:12:50.530 --> 00:12:52.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mmm. All the men I've known</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:12:53.147 --> 00:12:55.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>have needed to be shaped,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and molded, and manipulated</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:12:56.548 --> 00:12:57.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and finally I've met a man</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:12:58.446 --> 00:12:59.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>who knows how to do it himself.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:13:01.885 --> 00:13:03.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:13:04.985 --> 00:13:07.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning ) Is that the com?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I think it is. Excuse me.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:13:07.944 --> 00:13:09.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've got to get to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:13:25.859 --> 00:13:30.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Initiating high-resolution scan.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Memory nodes located.</i></c.bg_transparent>

233
00:13:30.937 --> 00:13:32.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Proceeding with data transfer.</i></c.bg_transparent>

234
00:13:33.656 --> 00:13:35.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeah, there you go.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Who would have thought?</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:13:35.856 --> 00:13:36.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You seem surprised, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:13:36.934 --> 00:13:38.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, knowing this computer,</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:13:38.215 --> 00:13:40.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought I would have had to reconfigure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the whole emulator module</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:13:40.856 --> 00:13:44.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to make it compatible with the probe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but it's cooperating for once.</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:13:46.174 --> 00:13:48.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Transfer of data is complete.</i></c.bg_transparent>

240
00:13:48.973 --> 00:13:50.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well done, computer.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:13:51.329 --> 00:13:54.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, run standard code translations</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on probe data.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:13:54.489 --> 00:13:55.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Isolate syntax results.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:13:56.488 --> 00:13:57.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Processing.</i></c.bg_transparent>

244
00:13:57.767 --> 00:13:58.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand by.</i></c.bg_transparent>

245
00:14:02.966 --> 00:14:04.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come in. Yes, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:14:05.005 --> 00:14:06.086 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander...</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:14:07.345 --> 00:14:09.086 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I have a problem.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Quark again?</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:14:09.285 --> 00:14:11.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, sir. This one is named Lwaxana.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:14:12.736 --> 00:14:13.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lwaxana Troi, the ambassador?</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:14:14.735 --> 00:14:15.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's her.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:14:15.843 --> 00:14:20.086 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was a minor incident at the bar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that I helped her with, and now she's...</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:14:21.401 --> 00:14:22.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Grateful.</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:14:23.080 --> 00:14:24.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's the problem?</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:14:24.499 --> 00:14:27.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The manner in which</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she expresses her... gratitude.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:14:28.539 --> 00:14:30.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To be honest, Commander, she seems...</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:14:31.698 --> 00:14:33.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Interested in me.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:14:35.476 --> 00:14:36.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's wrong with that?</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:14:38.335 --> 00:14:39.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's extremely aggressive.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:14:40.475 --> 00:14:42.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see. So she's after you.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:14:44.242 --> 00:14:45.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Like a Wanoni tracehound.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:14:45.973 --> 00:14:47.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you thought of letting her catch you?</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:14:48.773 --> 00:14:49.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir?</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:14:50.212 --> 00:14:51.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A little romance, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:14:52.558 --> 00:14:56.020 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have six pylons that need a complete</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>security sweep.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:14:56.030 --> 00:14:58.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't have time for romantic interludes.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:15:03.048 --> 00:15:05.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Frankly, in my humble opinion,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>most of you humanoids</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:15:05.630 --> 00:15:09.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>spend far too much time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on your respective mating rituals.</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:15:10.126 --> 00:15:12.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It does help the procreation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of one's species.</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:15:13.066 --> 00:15:16.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Procreation does not require</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>changing how you smell</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:15:16.424 --> 00:15:20.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>or writing bad poetry,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or sacrificing various plants</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:15:20.547 --> 00:15:22.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to serve as tokens of affection.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:15:24.422 --> 00:15:26.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In any event,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's all irrelevant to me.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:15:27.499 --> 00:15:28.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry to hear that.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:15:29.939 --> 00:15:33.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would appreciate it if you would do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>something about this woman.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:15:32.659 --> 00:15:33.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me?</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:15:33.959 --> 00:15:35.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just tell her to leave me alone.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:15:36.658 --> 00:15:40.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Constable, you can handle thieves</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and killers, but not one Betazoid woman?</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:15:40.837 --> 00:15:45.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand thieves and killers.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't understand... her.</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:15:46.235 --> 00:15:47.557 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't help you, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:15:47.795 --> 00:15:50.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm just trying to avoid</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a diplomatic incident.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:15:50.374 --> 00:15:52.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to insult the Ambassador.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:15:52.514 --> 00:15:53.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: A reasonable concern.</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:15:54.613 --> 00:15:57.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suggest you handle the matter</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with great delicacy.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:16:02.611 --> 00:16:06.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't handle "delicacy" very well.</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:16:10.188 --> 00:16:13.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The probe appears to be made out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of some sort of corundium alloy.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:16:14.250 --> 00:16:17.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Analysis of all subprocessor</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>modules is complete.</i></c.bg_transparent>

287
00:16:18.386 --> 00:16:18.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Already?</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:16:20.306 --> 00:16:21.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On screen.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:16:23.025 --> 00:16:24.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant?</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:16:28.542 --> 00:16:31.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No science modules</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>no communications system</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:16:31.903 --> 00:16:34.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and enough computer capacity to run</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a Galaxy-class starship.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:16:34.900 --> 00:16:36.020 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's very odd.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:16:36.601 --> 00:16:39.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's an awful lot of computer hardware</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>simply to navigate a probe.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:16:39.559 --> 00:16:40.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Anything?</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:16:41.612 --> 00:16:43.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing to suggest the probe's mission...</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:16:44.499 --> 00:16:45.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Or any hint of its origin.</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:16:54.256 --> 00:16:56.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah! There you are, Odo!</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:16:56.416 --> 00:17:00.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughs ) Have you ever been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the fourth moon of Andevian II at dawn?</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:17:00.534 --> 00:17:01.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can't say I have.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:17:01.616 --> 00:17:04.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have the most wonderful holoprogram.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And I've reserved a suite for us</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:17:04.132 --> 00:17:05.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>with that Quark person.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:17:05.811 --> 00:17:08.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You told Quark that you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were going into a holosuite with me?</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:17:08.490 --> 00:17:09.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, of course.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:17:09.950 --> 00:17:12.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's preparing a special</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>picnic basket for us.</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:17:12.030 --> 00:17:12.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good Lord.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:17:13.829 --> 00:17:15.050 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm afraid I'm not available.</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:17:15.050 --> 00:17:17.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to get</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to Upper Pylon 3 immediately.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:17:17.228 --> 00:17:18.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Madam Ambassador...</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:17:18.188 --> 00:17:19.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, Lwaxana.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:17:19.828 --> 00:17:22.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Um... Upper Pylon 3.</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:17:22.226 --> 00:17:24.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've always wanted to see an upper pylon.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:17:27.305 --> 00:17:31.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know, I'll have Quark</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>send one of his minions with our basket.</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:17:31.183 --> 00:17:32.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll have our picnic up there.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:17:32.544 --> 00:17:33.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Madam Ambassador...</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:17:33.663 --> 00:17:35.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, Lwaxana.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:17:35.842 --> 00:17:39.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't eat. This is not a real mouth.</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:17:39.423 --> 00:17:44.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is an approximation of one.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I do not have an esophagus or a stomach</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:17:44.026 --> 00:17:46.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or a digestive system. I am not like you.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:17:47.279 --> 00:17:51.582 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Every 16 hours, I turn into a liquid.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:17:52.597 --> 00:17:53.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can swim.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:17:53.717 --> 00:17:54.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh!</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:17:58.676 --> 00:17:59.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer?</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:18:00.835 --> 00:18:01.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer!</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:18:04.454 --> 00:18:05.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:18:06.013 --> 00:18:07.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:18:07.853 --> 00:18:10.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Ambassador Troi and I are stuck</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>in Turbolift 7.</i></c.bg_transparent>

327
00:18:10.332 --> 00:18:12.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>-What's going on?</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Power to the pylon</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:18:12.132 --> 00:18:13.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>turbolifts has failed.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:18:18.570 --> 00:18:22.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're reading a turbolift failure, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We'll beam you out.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:18:22.181 --> 00:18:23.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Locking on. Prepare to transport.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:18:24.460 --> 00:18:25.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Ready.</i></c.bg_transparent>

332
00:18:25.620 --> 00:18:26.819 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Energizing.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:18:32.898 --> 00:18:33.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well?</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:18:33.928 --> 00:18:35.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Looks like the transporter</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>is down, too.</i></c.bg_transparent>

335
00:18:35.804 --> 00:18:37.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>But don't worry, Constable.</i></c.bg_transparent>

336
00:18:37.084 --> 00:18:38.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We'll get it repaired right away.</i></c.bg_transparent>

337
00:18:40.504 --> 00:18:43.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax to Chief O'Brien.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Please report to Ops immediately.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:18:44.223 --> 00:18:45.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be patient, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:18:45.103 --> 00:18:47.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We'll get you out of there</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>as soon as we can.</i></c.bg_transparent>

340
00:18:49.861 --> 00:18:51.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, alone at last.</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:19:07.798 --> 00:19:09.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Electromotive</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>coil functions, normal.</i></c.bg_transparent>

342
00:19:09.976 --> 00:19:12.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Load detection functions, normal.</i></c.bg_transparent>

343
00:19:12.614 --> 00:19:13.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Diagnostic complete.</i></c.bg_transparent>

344
00:19:14.453 --> 00:19:15.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't get it.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:19:15.532 --> 00:19:19.071 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Every component of the turbolift power net</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>seems to be operational.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:19:19.252 --> 00:19:21.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can't find anything wrong</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the transporter.</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:19:21.971 --> 00:19:24.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Great, everything's in working order</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>except nothing's working.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:19:25.010 --> 00:19:26.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do we get our people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>out of the turbolift, Chief?</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:19:27.615 --> 00:19:29.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, if we were on a starship,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'd reroute the EPS power flow</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:19:30.028 --> 00:19:31.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>in a couple of hours,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but with this computer</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:19:31.827 --> 00:19:33.028 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>there's no telling how long it'll take.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:19:33.028 --> 00:19:33.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get it started.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:19:36.627 --> 00:19:37.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kira to Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:19:37.667 --> 00:19:38.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Yes, Major?</i></c.bg_transparent>

355
00:19:38.826 --> 00:19:40.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry, but you're going</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to have to stay put for a while longer.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:19:41.425 --> 00:19:42.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Define "a while."</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:19:43.746 --> 00:19:44.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish I knew.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:19:46.603 --> 00:19:48.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>By the way, Cardassian turbolifts</i></c.bg_transparent>

359
00:19:48.883 --> 00:19:51.084 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>run exposed, multi-phased</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>alternating currents</i></c.bg_transparent>

360
00:19:51.084 --> 00:19:52.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>through their positioning mechanisms</i></c.bg_transparent>

361
00:19:52.454 --> 00:19:54.509 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>so don't try to shape-shift your way out.</i></c.bg_transparent>

362
00:19:56.081 --> 00:19:56.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wouldn't think of it.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:19:59.399 --> 00:20:00.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Besides, it wouldn't be polite.</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:20:01.872 --> 00:20:02.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I didn't hear that.</i></c.bg_transparent>

365
00:20:04.798 --> 00:20:05.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I--It wouldn't be polite.</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:20:06.140 --> 00:20:08.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Understood. Kira out.</i></c.bg_transparent>

367
00:20:10.200 --> 00:20:11.559 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:20:10.640 --> 00:20:16.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you suppose that we're, uh...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we're actually in any danger?</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:20:16.720 --> 00:20:18.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not if we remain calm.</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:20:18.193 --> 00:20:18.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:20:18.180 --> 00:20:22.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, then we might as well</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>enjoy ourselves.</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:20:22.920 --> 00:20:26.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh, we can take the opportunity</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get to know each other.</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:20:26.780 --> 00:20:31.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd really prefer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to pass the time quietly.</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:20:31.340 --> 00:20:33.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Quietly.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Quietly.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:20:33.759 --> 00:20:35.059 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Of course.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:20:35.229 --> 00:20:36.028 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mmm.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:20:41.625 --> 00:20:42.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:20:42.880 --> 00:20:44.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The quiet man.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:20:51.920 --> 00:20:52.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:20:47.300 --> 00:20:50.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I've always been attracted to quiet men.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:20:50.780 --> 00:20:51.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odd, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:20:52.600 --> 00:20:56.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But maybe there's more truth than</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we realize to that old axiom that op--</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:21:03.867 --> 00:21:04.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quietly.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:21:15.672 --> 00:21:16.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:21:18.143 --> 00:21:19.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes?</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:21:20.143 --> 00:21:21.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't think I can.</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:21:24.461 --> 00:21:25.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can what?</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:21:25.741 --> 00:21:27.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, you don't have to say another word</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as long as we're here</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:21:27.520 --> 00:21:30.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I, I think I really need to talk.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:21:31.799 --> 00:21:32.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groans )</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:21:34.171 --> 00:21:34.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:21:40.826 --> 00:21:42.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's nothing to be afraid of.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:21:42.610 --> 00:21:43.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course not.</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:21:44.669 --> 00:21:46.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, things could be much worse.</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:21:47.067 --> 00:21:47.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really?</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:21:47.946 --> 00:21:49.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:21:49.726 --> 00:21:51.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My daughter and I were once trapped</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:21:51.427 --> 00:21:53.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>aboard a Ferengi cargo ship,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and it was dreadful.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:21:54.289 --> 00:21:57.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, all right,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it wasn't actually dreadful.</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:21:57.751 --> 00:21:59.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was mildly lamentable</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:21:59.950 --> 00:22:02.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and it was all because</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of that loathsome DaiMon.</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:22:02.909 --> 00:22:03.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well...</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:22:04.102 --> 00:22:06.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Actually, he wasn't altogether loathsome.</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:22:06.644 --> 00:22:08.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was just slightly repulsive.</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:22:10.302 --> 00:22:15.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But he did have a certain charm</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in an insufferable kind of way.</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:22:16.678 --> 00:22:20.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course, he was totally at the mercy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of his uncontrollable passion for me</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:22:20.797 --> 00:22:23.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>which means he wasn't all bad,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>now, doesn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:22:24.516 --> 00:22:27.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you know, it wasn't all passion, no.</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:22:27.573 --> 00:22:31.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was some negligible</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>commercial interest involved</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:22:31.295 --> 00:22:35.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but, oh, the passion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>oh, that was... that was perfectly real</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:22:36.864 --> 00:22:39.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and kind of, um, kind of sweet in a way.</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:22:39.911 --> 00:22:41.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was so helpless.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:22:43.092 --> 00:22:45.593 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>At first, it was totally</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a question of expediency</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:22:45.593 --> 00:22:47.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>when I made love with--with him.</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:22:47.397 --> 00:22:48.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you looking at?</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:22:49.676 --> 00:22:50.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm?</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:22:50.836 --> 00:22:51.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm?</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:22:51.715 --> 00:22:52.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh.</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:22:52.875 --> 00:22:53.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh, nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:22:54.555 --> 00:22:59.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was just wondering how many volts</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are in that exposed circuit.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:23:00.033 --> 00:23:01.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go on. Go on.</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:23:02.073 --> 00:23:05.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well... frankly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by the time one thing led to another...</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:23:07.983 --> 00:23:11.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Think of it as an opportunity, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You never know when a friendly ambassador</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:23:11.665 --> 00:23:14.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>is going to be in the right place</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the right time to help your career.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:23:14.664 --> 00:23:17.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Another hour with them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>could destroy my career.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:23:17.823 --> 00:23:21.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a simple job.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Just keep them happy and away from me.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:23:21.541 --> 00:23:22.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Simple?</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:23:22.781 --> 00:23:24.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing makes them happy.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:23:24.858 --> 00:23:26.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They are dedicated to being unhappy</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:23:26.699 --> 00:23:29.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and to spreading that unhappiness</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wherever they go.</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:23:29.257 --> 00:23:32.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They are the Ambassadors of Unhappy.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:23:32.055 --> 00:23:33.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:23:33.455 --> 00:23:35.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All of us have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>had these assignments, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:23:35.215 --> 00:23:36.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you, sir?</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:23:36.415 --> 00:23:39.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As a matter of fact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Curzon Dax used to take perverse pleasure</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:23:40.455 --> 00:23:41.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>in assigning me to take care</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of VIP guests.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:23:42.073 --> 00:23:44.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, so now you take the same</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>perverse pleasure.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:23:44.931 --> 00:23:45.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In doing it to me.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:23:46.532 --> 00:23:47.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Exactly.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:23:47.991 --> 00:23:48.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>May I ask, sir</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:23:49.210 --> 00:23:52.092 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>when you graduated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from this sort of assignment?</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:23:54.928 --> 00:23:57.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The day I hit one of the guests.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:23:58.168 --> 00:23:59.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hit one...</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:24:00.088 --> 00:24:03.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was a simple misunderstanding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>over his attempt to coax a young Ensign</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:24:03.127 --> 00:24:04.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to his quarters against her will.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:24:07.126 --> 00:24:07.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But...</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:24:10.204 --> 00:24:11.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't hit one of them, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:24:12.004 --> 00:24:14.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not nearly as understanding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as Curzon was.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:24:14.963 --> 00:24:16.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:24:17.202 --> 00:24:19.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O'Brien: Commander, can I talk to you?</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:24:22.681 --> 00:24:25.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-It's about the computer, sir.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Still giving you problems?</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:24:25.520 --> 00:24:27.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, sir, that's just the thing, it's not.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:24:27.519 --> 00:24:29.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It rerouted the EPS power flow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in less than an hour.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:24:29.998 --> 00:24:31.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's good news.</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:24:31.158 --> 00:24:33.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How soon can we get Odo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and the Ambassador out?</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:24:33.238 --> 00:24:36.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can't.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It didn't activate the turbolift circuits.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:24:36.180 --> 00:24:37.068 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't ask me why.</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:24:37.416 --> 00:24:39.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must have some idea of what's wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:24:40.375 --> 00:24:41.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to listen to something.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:24:42.434 --> 00:24:46.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, analyze Ops 0-2 sensor readings.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:24:47.953 --> 00:24:53.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>All sensors read between 14.3</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>and 14.4 KSC.</i></c.bg_transparent>

462
00:24:57.190 --> 00:25:01.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, restart all shield</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>generator subsystems.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:25:01.509 --> 00:25:04.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Shield generator subsystems</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>set to active status.</i></c.bg_transparent>

464
00:25:04.445 --> 00:25:06.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Reading 98.3% efficiency.</i></c.bg_transparent>

465
00:25:06.747 --> 00:25:08.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( whispering ) Do you hear it?</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:25:10.506 --> 00:25:11.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( whispering ) Hear what?</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:25:12.616 --> 00:25:14.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The voice, it's not the same attitude.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:25:15.024 --> 00:25:16.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It sounds like the computer.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:25:17.284 --> 00:25:19.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir, when you work</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with a computer as much as I do</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:25:19.205 --> 00:25:21.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you get to know it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They're all very different.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:25:22.322 --> 00:25:24.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Working with the</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Enterprise </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>computer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was like dancing a waltz.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:25:25.201 --> 00:25:27.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>With this computer, it's always</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>been like a wrestling match</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:25:27.881 --> 00:25:29.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>till we started downloading the probe.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:25:30.120 --> 00:25:32.221 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You think some kind of program</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the probe</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:25:32.221 --> 00:25:33.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>is influencing our computer?</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:25:33.980 --> 00:25:35.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, it's got to be more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than just a program, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:25:36.438 --> 00:25:38.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The computer's whole personality</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has changed.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:25:39.558 --> 00:25:41.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not resisting any commands</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:25:41.139 --> 00:25:43.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>offering any opinions,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>giving any arguments</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:25:44.536 --> 00:25:48.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and there's this one other crazy thing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm almost afraid to mention.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:25:48.815 --> 00:25:49.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's that?</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:25:50.834 --> 00:25:53.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Every time I leave</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>something happens to bring me back.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:25:53.953 --> 00:25:54.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bring you back?</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:25:54.913 --> 00:25:59.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To the computer like the failures</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the turbolifts and the transporters.</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:25:59.472 --> 00:26:01.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A few minutes ago, I was working</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the transporter pad</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:26:01.990 --> 00:26:05.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and the com lines went down</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and when I broke for a quick bite to eat</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:26:05.830 --> 00:26:07.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>we had a replicator failure.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:26:07.749 --> 00:26:11.028 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's almost like the computer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>doesn't want me to leave it alone.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:26:11.848 --> 00:26:13.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You almost make it sound like a child.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:26:23.555 --> 00:26:25.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Station Log, supplemental.</i></c.bg_transparent>

491
00:26:25.519 --> 00:26:27.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Odo and Ambassador Troi</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>remain trapped in Turbolift 4.</i></c.bg_transparent>

492
00:26:28.582 --> 00:26:31.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>As of yet, we have been unable</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to ascertain what it is</i></c.bg_transparent>

493
00:26:31.481 --> 00:26:34.043 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>that's causing the station's computer</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to malfunction.</i></c.bg_transparent>

494
00:26:34.961 --> 00:26:37.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if it's some kind</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of non biological life-form</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:26:37.760 --> 00:26:38.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>we've never seen before?</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:26:38.919 --> 00:26:38.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nonbiological?</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:26:41.059 --> 00:26:43.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, it all comes down</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to how we define life-form.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:26:43.798 --> 00:26:47.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But just as biological organisms</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have evolved in our cultures</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:26:47.617 --> 00:26:49.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>mechanical life could</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have done the same in others.</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:26:50.696 --> 00:26:53.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're suggesting someone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>left a baby at our doorstep.</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:26:54.215 --> 00:26:55.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Possibly.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:26:55.075 --> 00:26:56.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you think we can communicate with it?</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:26:56.834 --> 00:26:58.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, in a way, we already have.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:26:58.553 --> 00:27:00.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I mean, it's part and parcel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of our computer now.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:27:00.913 --> 00:27:03.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But as far as direct communication</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is concerned</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:27:03.115 --> 00:27:04.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it may not be capable of that.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:27:04.872 --> 00:27:07.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We haven't seen any evidence</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that this entity is sentient.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:27:07.554 --> 00:27:10.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: Maybe more like a stray puppy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's attached itself to you, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:27:10.733 --> 00:27:13.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Whatever it is, it's slowly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>disabling our station.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:27:13.209 --> 00:27:14.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>People, we've got to get it out of there.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:27:15.209 --> 00:27:18.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It came here when we downloaded</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the probe's files.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:27:18.747 --> 00:27:22.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we upload those same files back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the probe it might go with them.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:27:22.806 --> 00:27:25.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if it's fully integrated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>itself into our computer?</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:27:25.646 --> 00:27:28.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't think it has.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>That would make it more like a virus.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:27:28.725 --> 00:27:31.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I don't see any evidence</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that it's trying to overwrite</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:27:31.507 --> 00:27:33.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>our control networks or destroy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>our systems.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:27:34.284 --> 00:27:36.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think it's more likely that it simply</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>creates connections</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:27:36.806 --> 00:27:38.426 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>with areas of the computer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that are active.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:27:38.561 --> 00:27:41.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Almost as though it feeds off the energy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the computer functions.</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:27:41.960 --> 00:27:44.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I'm right, transferring</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all of its programming</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:27:44.662 --> 00:27:46.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>off the station might just solve</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>our problems.</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:27:51.878 --> 00:27:53.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How long since we had any communication</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from Odo?</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:27:54.257 --> 00:27:58.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Com lines have been down over 90 minutes.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He's been in there almost four hours now.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:27:59.835 --> 00:28:02.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you happen to know the schedule</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of his regenerative cycle?</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:28:02.735 --> 00:28:03.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My God, I have no idea</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:28:05.518 --> 00:28:07.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but if he doesn't get back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to his pail in time...</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:28:14.711 --> 00:28:19.549 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>COMPUTER:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Subspace emitter aligned.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Outgoing data stream activated.</i></c.bg_transparent>

528
00:28:20.254 --> 00:28:23.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, upload</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all probe command sequences</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:28:23.676 --> 00:28:24.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>back to probe's computer.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:28:25.928 --> 00:28:26.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stand by.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:28:27.687 --> 00:28:31.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Unable to complete requested function.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Please abort and retry.</i></c.bg_transparent>

532
00:28:32.526 --> 00:28:34.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reset subspace emitter.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:28:35.684 --> 00:28:36.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reinitialize data stream.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:28:38.142 --> 00:28:40.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Receptors open. Control relays activated.</i></c.bg_transparent>

535
00:28:43.272 --> 00:28:47.034 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Upload all probe command sequences</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>back to probe's computers.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:28:47.321 --> 00:28:48.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand by.</i></c.bg_transparent>

537
00:28:53.499 --> 00:28:56.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not as easy as I thought</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it would be, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:28:59.578 --> 00:29:03.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is it just the lights or the heat, too?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't bring any warm clothes.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:29:03.736 --> 00:29:05.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure it's just temporary.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:29:06.576 --> 00:29:10.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've been reading the reports</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of your Chief of Operations, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:29:10.974 --> 00:29:14.096 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They gave me the impression</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that he was a competent engineer.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:29:14.332 --> 00:29:16.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief O'Brien?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>One of the best in Starfleet.</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:29:17.152 --> 00:29:19.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then why aren't the backup</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>systems functioning?</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:29:19.791 --> 00:29:20.652 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, you know...</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:29:21.171 --> 00:29:25.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Out here on the edge of the frontier</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's just one adventure after another.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:29:26.130 --> 00:29:28.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why don't I escort you all back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to your quarters,</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:29:28.729 --> 00:29:31.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>where I'm sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we can all wait this one out.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:29:42.804 --> 00:29:44.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But enough about me.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:29:45.764 --> 00:29:46.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm?</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:29:47.143 --> 00:29:49.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Enough about me. Tell me about yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:29:52.377 --> 00:29:53.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm really a private man.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:29:55.801 --> 00:29:56.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, of course you are.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:30:00.799 --> 00:30:01.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that hair real?</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:30:04.758 --> 00:30:07.038 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is real in that it is me.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:30:08.117 --> 00:30:09.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is not real hair.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:30:11.385 --> 00:30:12.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How did you do it?</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:30:12.636 --> 00:30:13.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your hair.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:30:16.055 --> 00:30:17.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It took a great deal of practice.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:30:18.774 --> 00:30:20.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You studied hairstyles?</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:30:21.173 --> 00:30:22.053 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:30:23.406 --> 00:30:26.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you must know I imitated the hairstyle</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:30:26.531 --> 00:30:28.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>of the Bajoran man who was assigned to me.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:30:30.386 --> 00:30:30.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Assigned?</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:30:32.650 --> 00:30:37.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To study me at the research center.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He was a scientist.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:30:38.631 --> 00:30:41.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You mean that's how you grew up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in a laboratory?</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:30:43.726 --> 00:30:46.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did not grow up as you think of it.</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:30:47.565 --> 00:30:50.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was merely a transition</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from what I used to be...</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:30:52.043 --> 00:30:53.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To what I learned to become.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:30:55.042 --> 00:30:56.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh...</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:30:58.442 --> 00:31:00.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It sounds very lonely to me.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:31:04.180 --> 00:31:05.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was always very self-sufficient.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:31:08.179 --> 00:31:11.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure you had to be...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>uh, to survive...</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:31:12.257 --> 00:31:14.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Being... being so different</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from everyone else.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:31:19.016 --> 00:31:20.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:31:20.695 --> 00:31:21.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:31:22.815 --> 00:31:23.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Com lines are still down.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:31:24.646 --> 00:31:26.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know what's taking so long.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:31:26.765 --> 00:31:29.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you sure you're all right?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You look warm.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:31:29.543 --> 00:31:30.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's nothing. I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:31:34.926 --> 00:31:36.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, I can't imagine how it must have been.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:31:38.642 --> 00:31:40.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, if it bothers you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to talk about this...</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:31:40.532 --> 00:31:41.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not at all.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:31:43.828 --> 00:31:44.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What was it like?</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:31:45.488 --> 00:31:48.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess you could say</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I was the life of the party.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:31:49.979 --> 00:31:51.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't think I understand.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:31:51.866 --> 00:31:53.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My way of trying to fit in.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:31:54.465 --> 00:31:56.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I found I could be entertaining.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:31:57.305 --> 00:32:01.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Odo, be a chair." I'm a chair.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>"Odo, be a razorcat." I'm a razorcat.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:32:01.163 --> 00:32:02.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Life of the party.</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:32:02.923 --> 00:32:03.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckles )</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:32:04.682 --> 00:32:06.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hate parties.</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:32:08.660 --> 00:32:11.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, perhaps you've been going</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the wrong ones.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:32:13.480 --> 00:32:14.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come to one of mine, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:32:15.633 --> 00:32:18.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll make sure that all the guests</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are there to entertain you.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:32:22.177 --> 00:32:23.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groans )</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:32:23.417 --> 00:32:25.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, now, you're not well.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:32:26.775 --> 00:32:28.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, it's fine. It's just, uh...</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:32:32.354 --> 00:32:35.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I told you I turn into a liquid</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>every 16 hours.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:32:38.112 --> 00:32:40.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'm in hour 15.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:32:50.188 --> 00:32:51.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ready, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:32:51.348 --> 00:32:53.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How long do you expect it to take?</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:32:53.187 --> 00:32:54.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, if it works</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:32:54.109 --> 00:32:55.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>we ought to be able</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get all the probe's files</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:32:55.708 --> 00:32:58.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>manually transferred</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the six isolinear rods</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:32:57.987 --> 00:32:59.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>in less than 60 seconds.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:32:59.267 --> 00:33:00.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's do it.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:33:01.427 --> 00:33:05.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, run a level-1 diagnostic</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of all power systems on board.</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:33:05.584 --> 00:33:08.066 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Requested function</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>will require 43 minutes.</i></c.bg_transparent>

609
00:33:08.223 --> 00:33:09.103 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stand by.</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:33:11.265 --> 00:33:13.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Computer, give me an analysis</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:33:13.744 --> 00:33:15.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>of all Cardassian traffic</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>along the border.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:33:17.031 --> 00:33:19.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Processing long-range sensors. Stand by.</i></c.bg_transparent>

613
00:33:21.061 --> 00:33:23.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: Computer create</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a historical data base</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:33:23.741 --> 00:33:25.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for all known wormhole activity.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:33:25.820 --> 00:33:28.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( stuttering )</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Indicate time parameters.</i></c.bg_transparent>

616
00:33:28.099 --> 00:33:29.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: All known occurrences.</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:33:29.979 --> 00:33:34.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( slowly )</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Requested function</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>will require subspace link-up.</i></c.bg_transparent>

618
00:33:34.817 --> 00:33:38.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: In that case, create a subspace</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>link with Nehru Colony,</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:33:38.953 --> 00:33:42.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>New France Colony,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and Corado I Transmitter Array.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:33:43.433 --> 00:33:48.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( stuttering )</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Attempting link-up.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand by...</i></c.bg_transparent>

621
00:33:49.510 --> 00:33:53.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, access musical files</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Bajor Master Data Banks</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:33:53.012 --> 00:33:55.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and create a concert program</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of Bajoran serenas.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:33:55.612 --> 00:33:59.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand... by...</i></c.bg_transparent>

624
00:33:59.091 --> 00:34:02.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( fading )</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Unable to...</i></c.bg_transparent>

625
00:34:03.609 --> 00:34:04.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand...</i></c.bg_transparent>

626
00:34:07.489 --> 00:34:10.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm reading a huge plasma surge</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Habitat Ring.</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:34:11.084 --> 00:34:13.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You tell Commander Sisko that I expect</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that probe briefing</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:34:13.466 --> 00:34:16.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to be held on schedule,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>lights or no lights.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:34:16.082 --> 00:34:18.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I will surely pass that on, Ambassador--</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:34:22.080 --> 00:34:25.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got a plasma explosion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in corridor H-12-A, guest quarters.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:34:25.199 --> 00:34:26.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The computer's not responding.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:34:27.154 --> 00:34:28.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>None of the fire suppression</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>systems are coming on line.</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:34:28.377 --> 00:34:29.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm reading four life-forms</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in that corridor.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:34:30.379 --> 00:34:32.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Major, you're with me. Chief,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>get an emergency crew down there.</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:34:32.897 --> 00:34:34.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-We'll need manual fire gear.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:34:34.857 --> 00:34:36.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( coughing )</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:34:51.212 --> 00:34:55.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( coughing )</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:35:11.206 --> 00:35:13.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Phasers at maximum.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:35:17.738 --> 00:35:20.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Toranium inlay, Cardassian design</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I should have guessed.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:35:20.105 --> 00:35:22.085 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're going to need a bipolar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>torch to get through it.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:35:22.384 --> 00:35:23.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then get a message to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:35:23.585 --> 00:35:25.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell them it's going to take us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a while to get inside.</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:35:25.305 --> 00:35:27.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If they can't get the fire</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>suppression systems on line</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:35:27.414 --> 00:35:28.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>we're going to lose our people in there.</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:35:28.733 --> 00:35:29.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aye, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:35:32.221 --> 00:35:33.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not paying any attention to me.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:35:34.779 --> 00:35:38.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess it just doesn't want to leave</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>like a scared puppy.</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:35:40.097 --> 00:35:44.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have no idea how long that probe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was tumbling through space, maybe years,</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:35:44.396 --> 00:35:46.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>with that life-form alone on board.</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:35:46.716 --> 00:35:49.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's sort of like shutting up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a puppy in a room, you know?</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:35:51.025 --> 00:35:52.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had a pup once. If I had to lock him up</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:35:52.990 --> 00:35:54.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>he'd scratch forever</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the door trying to get out.</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:35:55.433 --> 00:35:57.034 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not sure I know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you're getting at.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:35:57.712 --> 00:36:00.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pups don't like to be left alone.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They like attention.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:36:01.471 --> 00:36:03.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This one is certainly getting a lot of it.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:36:03.870 --> 00:36:04.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:36:05.470 --> 00:36:07.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So it's no wonder</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it doesn't want to leave.</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:36:08.095 --> 00:36:09.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>OK, but how is that going to help us?</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:36:10.408 --> 00:36:11.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Everything we've seen suggests</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:36:11.729 --> 00:36:14.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that this entity likes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be where the action is.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:36:14.727 --> 00:36:17.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It seems to feed off the energy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of an active computer.</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:36:17.566 --> 00:36:20.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've been trying to separate it</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from what it thrives on.</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:36:21.205 --> 00:36:22.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got to do the exact opposite.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:36:23.484 --> 00:36:24.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The exact opposite?</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:36:25.084 --> 00:36:27.986 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant, I've got to build a doghouse.</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:36:29.722 --> 00:36:33.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( labored breathing )</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:36:39.200 --> 00:36:40.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo to Ops.</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:36:41.718 --> 00:36:42.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:36:46.078 --> 00:36:46.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo out.</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:36:47.517 --> 00:36:49.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo, turn around.</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:36:50.465 --> 00:36:52.796 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't. It's beginning.</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:36:53.835 --> 00:36:55.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right.</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:36:56.375 --> 00:36:57.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't understand.</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:36:58.854 --> 00:37:01.171 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No one has ever seen me like this before.</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:37:02.473 --> 00:37:04.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not even the scientist</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who was assigned to you?</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:37:05.271 --> 00:37:06.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That was different.</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:37:07.052 --> 00:37:08.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was only research to him.</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:37:10.610 --> 00:37:12.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you don't have to be ashamed with me.</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:37:13.449 --> 00:37:14.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not ashamed.</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:37:16.289 --> 00:37:18.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a private matter, that's all.</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:37:21.235 --> 00:37:22.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How can I make it easier for you?</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:37:24.326 --> 00:37:25.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't.</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:37:26.422 --> 00:37:26.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>

684
00:37:35.402 --> 00:37:36.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's that?</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:37:37.202 --> 00:37:38.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My hair.</c.bg_transparent>

686
00:37:47.213 --> 00:37:49.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No one's ever seen me like this.</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:37:50.938 --> 00:37:51.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:37:53.799 --> 00:37:54.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It looks fine.</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:37:56.816 --> 00:37:58.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It looks ordinary.</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:37:59.015 --> 00:38:00.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've never cared to be ordinary.</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:38:03.634 --> 00:38:06.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So you see, Odo,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>even we non-shape-shifters</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:38:06.374 --> 00:38:08.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>have to change who we are once in a while.</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:38:11.712 --> 00:38:14.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are not at all what I expected.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:38:18.587 --> 00:38:20.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No one's ever paid me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a greater compliment.</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:38:28.726 --> 00:38:32.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... cannot hold my shape any longer.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:38:36.684 --> 00:38:37.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let go.</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:38:40.324 --> 00:38:41.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll take care of you.</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:38:41.963 --> 00:38:43.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:38:50.720 --> 00:38:54.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: We're going to need portable</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>oxygen and get anything</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:38:54.200 --> 00:38:57.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bashir has in stock to treat plasma burns.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Have a runabout ready</c.bg_transparent>

701
00:38:57.162 --> 00:38:58.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to evacuate these people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to Bajor if we need to.</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:38:58.881 --> 00:38:59.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

703
00:39:02.800 --> 00:39:03.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Anara?</c.bg_transparent>

704
00:39:04.319 --> 00:39:05.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The subprogram is ready, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

705
00:39:06.655 --> 00:39:09.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, analyze subprogram</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>labeled "Pup."</c.bg_transparent>

706
00:39:11.066 --> 00:39:14.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Requested subprogram is a series</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>of bi-directional data transfer</i></c.bg_transparent>

707
00:39:14.648 --> 00:39:15.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>and monitoring commands.</i></c.bg_transparent>

708
00:39:16.532 --> 00:39:20.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reroute all main computer backup functions</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>through this subprogram.</c.bg_transparent>

709
00:39:21.411 --> 00:39:23.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>All backup functions rerouted.</i></c.bg_transparent>

710
00:39:24.050 --> 00:39:24.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Great.</c.bg_transparent>

711
00:39:25.909 --> 00:39:27.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>OK, computer. Now, listen carefully.</c.bg_transparent>

712
00:39:28.589 --> 00:39:31.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want to transfer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all probe command sequences</c.bg_transparent>

713
00:39:31.448 --> 00:39:34.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>out of core memory</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and into the subprogram Pup.</c.bg_transparent>

714
00:39:34.687 --> 00:39:36.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Stand by.</i></c.bg_transparent>

715
00:39:38.787 --> 00:39:39.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Transfer complete.</i></c.bg_transparent>

716
00:39:42.185 --> 00:39:44.767 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Dax to Sisko.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Fire suppression is responding.</i></c.bg_transparent>

717
00:39:44.767 --> 00:39:46.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>All systems are back on line.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Can you get in?</i></c.bg_transparent>

718
00:39:50.925 --> 00:39:52.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're in, Dax. Stand by.</c.bg_transparent>

719
00:39:54.803 --> 00:39:57.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( electrical hissing and popping )</c.bg_transparent>

720
00:40:13.184 --> 00:40:14.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'd better advise Starfleet Command.</c.bg_transparent>

721
00:40:15.574 --> 00:40:16.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( rattling )</c.bg_transparent>

722
00:40:20.413 --> 00:40:21.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you all right?</c.bg_transparent>

723
00:40:22.412 --> 00:40:24.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: Here, take my hand,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Madam Ambassador.</c.bg_transparent>

724
00:40:25.733 --> 00:40:26.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Watch your head.</c.bg_transparent>

725
00:40:28.812 --> 00:40:29.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

726
00:40:30.331 --> 00:40:31.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Call me Taxco.</c.bg_transparent>

727
00:40:33.349 --> 00:40:34.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ambassador, are you all right?</c.bg_transparent>

728
00:40:34.749 --> 00:40:36.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes. Thanks to Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

729
00:40:40.967 --> 00:40:44.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Doctor</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was remarkably calm and logical,</c.bg_transparent>

730
00:40:44.169 --> 00:40:47.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>for a man of his years,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>under such severe conditions.</c.bg_transparent>

731
00:40:47.825 --> 00:40:49.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll be putting him</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in for a commendation.</c.bg_transparent>

732
00:40:54.423 --> 00:40:55.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nice work, Dr. Bashir.</c.bg_transparent>

733
00:40:57.063 --> 00:40:58.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just in the right place</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the right time, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

734
00:41:06.579 --> 00:41:08.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, it's about time.</c.bg_transparent>

735
00:41:11.299 --> 00:41:15.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... know that wasn't exactly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you had in mind</c.bg_transparent>

736
00:41:15.922 --> 00:41:16.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for your picnic.</c.bg_transparent>

737
00:41:18.956 --> 00:41:22.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When it comes to picnics</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the only thing that really matters</c.bg_transparent>

738
00:41:22.235 --> 00:41:23.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>is the company.</c.bg_transparent>

739
00:41:24.674 --> 00:41:28.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your sensitivity and discretion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are appreciated.</c.bg_transparent>

740
00:41:29.913 --> 00:41:30.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well...</c.bg_transparent>

741
00:41:32.712 --> 00:41:35.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Next time you see me I'll give you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a lot more to appreciate.</c.bg_transparent>

742
00:41:48.247 --> 00:41:50.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How did you beat that thing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the computer, Chief?</c.bg_transparent>

743
00:41:51.506 --> 00:41:53.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I didn't.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-He adopted it.</c.bg_transparent>

744
00:41:53.486 --> 00:41:54.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Adopted it?</c.bg_transparent>

745
00:41:54.346 --> 00:41:55.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I was able to get our friend</c.bg_transparent>

746
00:41:55.567 --> 00:41:57.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>out of the main command pathways</c.bg_transparent>
