748
00:42:01.403 --> 00:42:03.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's happy. It's not bothering us anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

749
00:42:04.309 --> 00:42:05.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, it seems the humane thing to do.</c.bg_transparent>

750
